body\">Is an excellent module focus on customizing the WordPress login. frequently used in many installations like a default customize part of a website.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Plug &amp; Play</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/connor11493/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/641e8cba2d5d66d210ac39a8c289ff9d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/641e8cba2d5d66d210ac39a8c289ff9d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/connor11493/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Connor Levens <small>(connor11493)</small></a> el <span class=\"review-date\">mayo 23, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Excellent, lightweight plugin with many customizable features make Colorlib\'s Coming Soon plugin the ideal choice for someone looking to quickly throw users a splash page with the flip of a switch.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 